{"tid":1912584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[奇怪］一道緊急調令，10箱應急物資從武漢運抵北京","createTime":"2020-03-06T07:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T18:30:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d4b48610fbeebc9ef0cea24aef7273dc1767c12e","tid":1912584,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rRp32y0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrRp32y0.jpg&h=17609915&s={SIZE}\" />3月4日16時37分許，在交通運輸部緊急運輸任務指令保障下，中國紅十字會10箱緊急物資從湖北省武漢市通過鐵路方式順利起運。<br />\n<br />\n當日13時30分許，交通運輸部物流保障辦公室接到一項緊急運輸需求&mdash;&mdash;中國紅十字會需從武漢市運輸10箱緊急物資至北京市。<br />\n<br />\n值班工作人員立即詳細瞭解運輸需求，聯繫各有關方研究保障方案，隨後發出第47號緊急運輸指令，協調國家鐵路集團承擔緊急運輸任務。<br />\n<br />\n國家鐵路集團第一時間安排鐵路運力，組織中鐵快運全力做好10箱緊急物資的運輸保障工作。據瞭解，這批緊急物資預計今夜抵達北京西站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202003/04/WS5e5faf8ce4b05d1eff0b4993.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bjd.com.cn%2Fa%2F202003%2F04%2FWS5e5faf8ce4b05d1eff0b4993.html&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=bab51565\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202003/04/WS5e5faf8ce4b05d1eff0b4993.html</a><br />\n<br />\n竟然由重災區搬物資去北京？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf3b6535aa487e80b1571ddbe46ccb9105d97c5","tid":1912584,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3040920335952733&amp;id=142135802497882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3040920335952733%26id%3D142135802497882&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=5eb28b20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3040920335952733&amp;id=142135802497882</a>"},{"pid":"8bc188cab1fcbae7c8922b3248f72bfcb66c116e","tid":